snippet.title: Showbiz Minute: Diana, Oscars, Heard
snippet.description:
Princes William, Harry unveil Princess Diana statue; Oscars invite Steven Yeun, Issa Rae, others to join Academy; Amber Heard is mom "on my own terms" with baby girl Oonagh. (July 2)
